Every year Mr. Wyman and coaches produce an end of the year Viking Wrestling Video. This year, they thought they will share a little sunshine for your day and recognize staff of D56 for the part they played in the D56 wrestling team success. It was truly a historic year of wrestling. It was historic not because the IESA State Finals was cancelled. It was historic because the team tied a record for qualifying the most wrestlers for the State Finals - 9 wrestlers!

Enjoy the video!
